1
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:41,160
Xiaoxue.

2
00:00:42,160 --> 00:00:42,960
What's wrong?

3
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,980
How did you get hurt like this?

4
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,610
Already feeling sorry for her?

5
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:51,840
She is

6
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,040
fine right now.

7
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:55,960
But who knows about later.

8
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,560
What else do you want?

9
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,200
What exactly are you trying to do?

10
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,120
What I want to do

11
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,680
is none of your business.

12
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:03,200
As long as you

13
00:01:04,360 --> 00:01:05,760
do exactly as I say now,

14
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:07,320
I won't hurt her.

15
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:09,880
Otherwise...

16
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:11,340
I'll do anything you want,

17
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,520
as long as you don't hurt her.

18
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:14,980
Please don't hurt her.

19
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:16,520
Good.

20
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:18,960
This magic array,

21
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,160
lie on it yourself.

22
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:21,770
Okay.

23
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:22,680
I will.

24
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:23,560
I will.

25
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:25,410
Just don't hurt her.

26
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:45,820
Daoist Master.

27
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:50,080
Can I finally see you again?

28
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,440
Brother Wuzhou.

29
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,330
Young Master

30
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,479
Li.

31
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,890
They haven't come back yet.

32
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,080
It seems

33
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,440
there is no news.

34
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,400
Lu Danyu.

35
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:11,280
The soul of the Child of the World is imprisoned.

36
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,640
My connection with him is about to be disconnected.

37
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,640
Things are bad.

38
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,480
Yiyi.

39
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,780
What's wrong with your voice?

40
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,020
From now on,

41
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,600
I'm afraid I can hardly maintain your body.

42
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:23,240
What?

43
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,060
How could this happen?

44
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,680
I'm sorry.

45
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,240
The identity I gave you

46
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,360
doesn't exist in the subsequent timeline.

47
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,200
So...

48
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:50,880
Are you saying

49
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,600
the moment I arrived,

50
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:56,960
she had already...

51
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,280
Yes.

52
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,720
I see.

53
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,240
So,

54
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,600
am I going back?

55
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,840
If I completely disconnect from the Child of the World,

56
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,400
before returning to the source,

57
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,530
I will send you back.

58
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,360
What do you mean by returning to the source?

59
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,840
I will return to the source as an energy form

60
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,840
and will no longer have consciousness.

61
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:57,640
What?

62
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,280
Then wouldn't you...

63
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,000
Can you not go back?

64
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,410
Having lost the Child of the World,

65
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,560
if I don't return to the source,

66
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,290
the world will suffer greatly.

67
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,440
Yiyi.

68
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:20,519
If I find Brother Wuzhou...

69
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,240
I can't sense him.

70
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,120
What about Sister Mu?

71
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,520
Even earlier,

72
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,650
I tried to sense her.

73
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,090
I couldn't find her.

74
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,440
Try again.

75
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,370
There might be a different result.

76
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,159
She...

77
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,480
is in Yuelun Village.

78
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,240
Look, Yiyi.

79
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,760
We found her.

80
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,880
Don't give up.

81
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,010
There is still a chance.

82
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,740
What's wrong with you?

83
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,200
I'm a little obsessed.

84
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,880
I found Sister Mu.

85
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,120
She is in Yuelun Village.

86
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,650
Let's go.

87
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,440
Is she that important to you?

88
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,780
Even like this,

89
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,500
you still want to save her.

90
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:35,960
Not just her.

91
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,080
Anyone I care about

92
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,860
is very important.

93
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:43,600
And that

94
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,560
includes you.

95
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,120
As long as you don't harm this world,

96
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:53,040
you are also a very important person

97
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,120
in my life.

98
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,680
Glib.

99
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,080
This little blood

100
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,760
is just interest.

101
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,960
How can we find a flower demon that has been hiding for 30 years?

102
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,420
And it's just the few of us.

103
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,640
Exactly.

104
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:42,120
We still don't have any clues about the Demon King,

105
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,580
and now we have to look for some flower demon.

106
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,280
I know, right?

107
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,640
It's been so long,

108
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,100
and we have no clues at all.

109
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,880
I wonder if the teams in other places

110
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,340
have any new information.

111
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,680
Putting everything else aside,

112
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,800
The sect is taking

113
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,159
the search for the Demon King

114
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,620
very seriously this time.

115
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,600
Just for clues,

116
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,920
they gave out a lot of sect rewards.

117
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:06,600
Not to mention capturing or injuring the Demon King.

118
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,280
I get so envious

119
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,340
just looking at it.

120
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,520
What do you guys think?

121
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,720
We've searched this area so many times.

122
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,800
We should have moved on a long time ago.

123
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,560
I didn't expect

124
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,520
that we'd suddenly stay to look for some flower demon.

125
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,520
Exactly.

126
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:21,920
They couldn't find the flower demon in 30 years.

127
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,760
We just got here.

128
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:23,840
Can we find it?

129
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,290
Stop talking nonsense.

130
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,840
This is a mission from the palace.

131
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:32,440
Whether we can find it or not,

132
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,720
let's just search first.

133
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,280
Chunyi,

134
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,840
there are still no clues about Lanqi and Moyuan.

135
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:39,040
Why are we wasting time in a place like this?

136
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,720
The flower demon that harms the human world

137
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:43,360
is the primary target for our Tiandao Palace to eliminate.

138
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,560
Our fundamental duty

139
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,880
is to maintain peace in the human world.

140
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:47,850
Alright.

141
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,460
Stop complaining.

142
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,380
Get to work.

143
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:50,960
Yes.

144
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,800
You got here so fast.
